column2: SELECT s.plate,s.mjd,s.fiberid,s.z,s.zErr,s.zWarning,s.class,p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj,cast(str(p.ra,#,#) as float) as ra,cast(str(p.[dec],#,#) as float) as dec,p.r,p.u,p.g,p.i,p.z,p.psfMag_u,p.psfMag_g,p.psfMag_r,p.psfMag_i,p.psfMag_z,p.petroMag_u,p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,dbo.fIAUFromEq(p.ra,p.[dec]) as SDSSname  FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN RUN AS r ON p.run=r.run WHERE r.stripe = # and s.class=QSO AND s.zWarning = # AND p.u < # AND p.g < # AND p.r < # AND p.i < # AND p.z < # AND ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)
